data.description: Gorgeous 3-level colonial on large fenced lot. Impeccable condition. The main level features entry hall with powder room and cedar lined coat closet; separate living room with 2 windows, gleaming hardwood floors and gas fireplace with mantel; chef's kitchen with gas cooktop, stainless appliances, hardwood floors and walkout to multi-level deck plus access to 2-car garage.  Upper level features primary bedroom with custom closet, ceiling fan and en suite updated bath;  2nd and 3rd bedrooms with ceiling fans and custom closets plus full hall bath with tub shower. Lower level is fully finished with recreation room, 4th bedroom and 3rd full bath. Keypad entry to 2-car garage. Large, terraced and fenced backyard.
